From: L. David Baron <dbaron@dbaron.org>

Fix missing PropagateGrandancestorBit.

This probably isn't needed today because both callers of
nsStyleContext::HasChildThatUsesGrandancestorStyle also check for line
frames, but it seems better to have this bit set correctly in case we
use it for something else.

